
                                Run container without docker-compose             [very tedious to run]
                              *************************************************************************
Run  container
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
> docker run 
_________________________________________________________________________


*****************************************************************************************************************
                              Run container with docker-compose             [very EASY to run]
                             *************************************************************************
configure automatically using "docker-compose.yml   // running docker containers
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
> docker-compose up 
_________________________________________________________________________
Configure the same in Detached Mode    [Note : runs in background]
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
> docker-compose up -d
_________________________________________________________________________
 To see what all dockers are running
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------
> docker ps
_________________________________________________________________________
To stop the running docker  containers           [ Note: ctrl + C won't work]
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
> docker-compose stop
_________________________________________________________________________



*****************************************************************************************************************
